					<description><![CDATA[<p><img width="2560" height="1707" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/dagmar-klauzova-s9A6HD8KC5Q-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/dagmar-klauzova-s9A6HD8KC5Q-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/dagmar-klauzova-s9A6HD8KC5Q-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/dagmar-klauzova-s9A6HD8KC5Q-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/dagmar-klauzova-s9A6HD8KC5Q-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1365&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/dagmar-klauzova-s9A6HD8KC5Q-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=219%2C146&amp;ssl=1 219w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/dagmar-klauzova-s9A6HD8KC5Q-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導 近日國外發生一起暖心的寵物故事，一隻名叫「溫迪（Wendy）」的小貓不僅迅速融 &#8230;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/08/23/%e8%b7%a8%e8%b6%8a%e7%a8%ae%e6%97%8f%e7%9a%84%e5%8f%8b%e8%aa%bc%ef%bc%81%e5%a4%a7%e7%8b%97%e8%88%87%e5%b0%8f%e5%a5%b6%e8%b2%93%e4%b8%80%e8%a6%8b%e5%a6%82%e6%95%85%e6%88%90%e7%82%ba%e6%9c%80%e5%a5%bd/">跨越種族的友誼！大狗與小奶貓一見如故成為最好的朋友 </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img width="2560" height="1707" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/dagmar-klauzova-s9A6HD8KC5Q-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/dagmar-klauzova-s9A6HD8KC5Q-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/dagmar-klauzova-s9A6HD8KC5Q-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/dagmar-klauzova-s9A6HD8KC5Q-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/dagmar-klauzova-s9A6HD8KC5Q-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1365&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/dagmar-klauzova-s9A6HD8KC5Q-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=219%2C146&amp;ssl=1 219w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/dagmar-klauzova-s9A6HD8KC5Q-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導</p>



<p>近日國外發生一起暖心的寵物故事，一隻名叫「溫迪（Wendy）」的小貓不僅迅速融入新環境，還與家中重達135磅的大狗「喬治（George）」建立起跨物種的深厚情誼，意外地治癒這戶人家的心，幫助他們走出愛寵離世的悲痛。&nbsp;</p>



<p>據了解，「溫迪」原本是一隻在外頭流浪的貓咪，在不久前被這戶好心的家庭收養，起初飼主還擔心小貓會因為體型差距而害怕家中的大狗「喬治」，但令人意外的是，「溫迪」一見到「喬治」便感到親近依賴，無論走到哪裡都跟隨在牠身邊。&nbsp;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1220" height="1627" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/louis-philippe-poitras-sJgucUmcaKE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1220%2C1627&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-245712" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/louis-philippe-poitras-sJgucUmcaKE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=1920&amp;ssl=1 1920w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/louis-philippe-poitras-sJgucUmcaKE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/louis-philippe-poitras-sJgucUmcaKE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1152%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1152w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/louis-philippe-poitras-sJgucUmcaKE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C2048&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/louis-philippe-poitras-sJgucUmcaKE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=110%2C146&amp;ssl=1 110w" sizes="(max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">「溫迪」的到來治癒了「喬治」的內心，成為最要好的夥伴<br>(示意圖/Unsplash)</figcaption></figure>



<p>隨著時間流逝，如今「喬治」已經完全成為了「溫迪」最要好的家人，牠常常會用尾巴陪伴小貓玩耍，耐心地呵護這位新夥伴，對此飼主表示，這一幕對全家人來說格外動人，因為在不久前他們才經歷過一隻愛寵的離世，牠曾與「喬治」一同長大，情同手足，也因此讓「喬治」陷入好長一段時間的低落與孤單。&nbsp;</p>



<p>幸好「溫迪」的到來成為一份療癒的禮物，小貓帶來的活力與依戀，不僅幫助「喬治」重新打開心門，也讓全家人走出失去愛寵的悲傷，故事曝光後讓許多網友感動留言「可能是上天的安排」、「喬治現在有了溫迪」、「沒有誰能被取代，但愛會被延續」。&nbsp;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/08/23/%e8%b7%a8%e8%b6%8a%e7%a8%ae%e6%97%8f%e7%9a%84%e5%8f%8b%e8%aa%bc%ef%bc%81%e5%a4%a7%e7%8b%97%e8%88%87%e5%b0%8f%e5%a5%b6%e8%b2%93%e4%b8%80%e8%a6%8b%e5%a6%82%e6%95%85%e6%88%90%e7%82%ba%e6%9c%80%e5%a5%bd/">跨越種族的友誼！大狗與小奶貓一見如故成為最好的朋友 </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
